name: WestJet Frozen Livery 737-8CT [C-GWSV] Sunrise Takeoff from Calgary Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
I haven't filmed WestJet's special liveries nearly often enough. Here we have their Frozen themed airplane departing Calgary International Airport for an early morning flight to Toronto as WS658. Some fantastic lighting too! ATC is included, enjoy.

Thanks for watching!
